OL,2,MBehind the Curtain: Inside the Hidden
OL,4,MTech of Live Theatre and Events
OL,6,CJon Kingsley
OL,7,CSat 13:30-14:00
OL,8,CStage A
OL,10,GWhat happens when the lights go out,
OL,11,Gthe flames shoot up, and the performer
OL,12,Gflies over the audience? None of it is
OL,13,Gmagic - it’s a remarkably deep stack
OL,14,Gof engineering, software, and
OL,15,Gcontrolled chaos, and almost none of
OL,16,Git is visible to the audience. This
OL,17,Gtalk pulls back the curtain on the
OL,18,Gtechnology powering professional
OL,19,Gtheatre and live events - from West
OL,20,GEnd productions to outdoor festivals.
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
